items.title: Olive Green Cabled Crewneck
items.description: A textured diamond pattern lends character to a cotton crewneck sweater knit with unexpected wide sleeves.

items.title: Flare Jeans
items.description: Fitted through the waist and flared at the legs, these stretchy, full-length jeans have sleek center pintucks and welt pockets for an updated look.

items.title: Pleated Midi Skirt
items.description: An elastic waist tops this flowy midi-length skirt accented with a layered design, asymmetric hem and easy-moving pleats.

items.title: Floral Midi Dress
items.description: Prairie style goes contemporary on this floral midi with a button-up bodice, a drawstring waist and a ruffle-tiered skirt interrupted by a front slit.

items.title: Olive Green Cotton T-Shirt
items.description: A laid-back slub-knit T-shirt is made of organic cotton and washed for amazing softness.

items.title: Straight Leg Jeans
items.description: Tried-and-true straight-leg jeans in a versatile wash are made from soft, shape-retaining stretch denim to move with you from day to night.

items.title: Gray Crewneck Sweater
items.description: Luxuriously soft and endlessly versatile, this crewneck sweater is knit from soft cashmere yarns you'll appreciate from the work week to the weekend.

items.title: White Dress Shirt
items.description: Stay comfy as you transition from office hours to happy hour in a streamlined button-up cut from a fresh cotton blend enriched with moisture-wicking fibers.

items.title: Faux Leather Laptop Bag
items.description: Conquer your KPIs from anywhere with the Laptop Bag.

items.title: Leather Belt
items.description: Burnished leather with a sophisticated patina elevates this Italian-crafted belt finished with a square buckle.

items.title: Sunglasses
items.description: Signature T-hardware details the temples of these Italian-made sunglasses designed with a keyhole bridge that brings retro appeal.
